'''Wolfgang Dehen''' (born 9 February 1954) is the [[CEO]] of the [[Siemens Energy Sector|Energy Sector]] of [[Siemens]].<ref>{{Cite web|url =http://w1.siemens.com/press/en/pp_cc/2007/11_nov/sosep200734-01.htm| title = CEO of the Energy Sector and Member of the Managing Board of Siemens AG| accessdate=2008-03-15}}</ref> Born in [[Solingen]] he studied [[Business Administration]] at the [[University of Siegen]], Germany.<ref>{{Cite web| url =http://investing.businessweek.com/businessweek/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=24271810&capId=394038&previousCapId=394038&previousTitle=Siemens%20AG |title= Business Week| accessdate=2008-03-15}}</ref>
